{"tid":1348423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗友、沙田友、番屋企","createTime":"2019-07-22T08:10:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T08:29:21.000Z","uid":259140,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"97ddf057a4f8f55d115978fd7a08322aefd0dbb2","tid":1348423,"uid":259140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:10:47.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪堅<br />\n安全最重要<br />\nBe water<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wBUbqrv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwBUbqrv.png&h=7bd11ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BCiSUjR.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBCiSUjR.png&h=5d672dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n重要！<br />\n傳聞已確認<br />\n<br />\n今日元朗有位白衫叔父香左<br />\n網上傳係「心臟病發」<br />\n老黑傳係「比人用較剪隊中左」<br />\n<br />\n聽日會吹大雞黎料，有曬架生（firm左）<br />\n<br />\n唔好指意差佬，死撚緊<br />\n如在元朗番工既朋友聽日最好請假<br />\n住元朗既朋友最好避免出街<br />\n<br />\n90% confirm<br />\n元朗站 會有班尼泊爾仔上刀見人就斬<br />\n<br />\n任何人唔好去果頭！"},{"pid":"e5fa75a209df3d33171b22f5253db991e29242de","tid":1348423,"uid":100016,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:12:48.000Z","msg":"唔知係咪堅<br />\n傳聞已確認<br />\n<br />\n善用起底功能。"},{"pid":"cb1d4072628b5299a6d073f7cbedfbe72f76e160","tid":1348423,"uid":130901,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:15:10.000Z","msg":"區區有黑幫，太多傳聞，一定係有人故意放風"},{"pid":"0afe9fbe5784163ffdc2b8b3f6e916444dd95894","tid":1348423,"uid":3786,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:16:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"></span>沙田大圍馬鞍山<br />\n你當我傻？<br />\n大圍劈入去馬鞍山仲遠撚過當年dum碌鳩落街呀[/red]</strong></span>"},{"pid":"e43cfff40b7810aed5ea73d39448367af9e4b513","tid":1348423,"uid":272569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T08:17:02.000Z","msg":"所有元朗人即刻走！走唔到留室內！流浮山有200刀手落緊元朗！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1347479\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1347